      <title>印尼总统将在与特朗普会晤前访问习近平</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/indonesia-s-prabowo-to-visit-xi-before-possible-trump-meeting</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼总统普拉博沃·苏比安托将于周五会见中国国家主席习近平，然后前往美国与当选总统唐纳德·特朗普举行会晤，在他首次出访期间平衡与世界两大经济体的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/indonesia-s-prabowo-to-visit-xi-before-possible-trump-meeting</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 23:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
